    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im struggling to breathe a bit after being at the park... i keep wheezing and it's making it hard to get air in. i think it's just my hay fever acting up bc of the pollen. do u think i should just take an antihistamine like zyrtec to stop it?",
