      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just a bit of a whistling sound when i breathe, nothing crazy. i don't want to go to the doctor if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. like, if i take two zyrtec instead of one, will that definitely clear it up so i can sleep tonight? i really just need it to stop so i can rest.",
